snippet.title: Unicycle Giraffe Trailer
snippet.description:
Unicycle Giraffe a balancing game about giraffes, fancy hats & making new friends. Jump on a unicycle and earn yourself some coin to pay back your debts in this cute and colourful physics wobbler.  

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/unicycle-giraffe/id1400597176
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MassiveMonster.Unicycle_Giraffe

Why You'll love it! 
- High-tech giraffe physics simulation technology
- Collect new friends! 
- Unlock skins such as Spider Giraffe & Frog Giraffe
- The giraffe has a nice shade of yellow
